research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32128:research/history/round_summaries/round_0040.json:75:    "self_review": "满足 repair 约束：未改 family_name，未改 env_overrides，仍是相对 r27 只切到 `ARCHITECTURE=two_stage_residual_expert`。根因已确认是 `Unknown architecture`，并已完成 checklist 所需的 whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke。显式 dispatch smoke 在 `(architecture=two_stage_residual_expert, K=192, EF=1)` 上通过，selection_cost≈0.31x、deployment≈0.19x、total≈0.50x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.33，仍在 LUTurbo 成本硬约束内。override 校验也已通过，下一次真实运行不应再卡在 parse/dispatch 阶段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32146:research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r\uff1b{u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r205-r206 \u5df2\u628a `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5728 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` \u8fd9\u6761 lane \u7684 coarse/cleanup \u5206\u5de5\u57fa\u672c\u6478\u6e05\uff1a`STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` \u867d\u628a objective \u4ece 0.398672 \u538b\u5230 0.396941\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u672a\u8d8a\u8fc7 r159 \u7684 0.395234\uff0c\u66f4\u6ca1\u6709\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent 0.386114\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u8fd9\u6761 family \u4e0a\u505a budget split \u7ec6\u626b\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\u4ef7\u503c\u5df2\u7ecf\u660e\u663e\u4e0b\u964d\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r201 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cshared coarse + routed residual cleanup\u201d\u76f8\u6bd4\u201clow-rank trunk + expert head\u201d\u5230\u5e95\u662f\u4e0d\u662f\u5f53\u524d 0.20x \u5de6\u53f3 lane \u7684\u6b63\u786e\u5bb9\u91cf\u5206\u5de5\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\uff0c\u8be5\u5019\u9009\u7684 combined_accesses=835584\u3001actual total_cost_ratio\u22480.199219x\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e r201/r206 \u7684 0.210938x\uff1b\u5982\u679c exceed \u4ecd\u80fd\u7ef4\u6301\u5728\u8be5 family \u5df2\u77e5\u7684\u7ea6 0.188 \u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u5219 objective \u5c06\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u538b\u5230 0.39 \u9644\u8fd1\u5e76\u6311\u6218\u5f53\u524d\u6b21\u4f18\u517c\u5bb9\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32147:research/history/round_summaries/round_0207.json:36:      "\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u5df2\u901a\u8fc7\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk K=64 A=2 L=160 TRUNK_RANK=16` \u7684 selection_accesses=425984\u3001deployment_accesses=409600\u3001combined_accesses=835584\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u7684 actual total_cost_ratio\u22480.199219x\uff1b\u8fd9\u6bd4 r201/r206 \u7684 0.210938x \u66f4\u4f4e\uff0c\u4e14\u4ecd\u5904\u5728\u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32158:research/history/logs/agent_action_0153.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库 local top-k + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，所有库都为静态向量库、不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不得进入 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r152 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“全局 residual cleanup 是否足以支撑单 expert 激活路径”，从而把当前低成本最佳点从约 0.49x 进一步压到约 0.44x total_cost，同时尽量维持优于现有低成本前沿的 FVU。","summary":"建议以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。这不是继续细扫 `K` 轴，而是对当前最强低成本结构做一次更有结构信息的 matched-cost probe：验证 residual 补偿是否能让 `lowrank_expert_residual` 承受单 expert 路径，把总成本从约 0.49x 压到约 0.44x。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。之所以不继续顺着 `K` 做第三轮局部下压，是因为提示已明确要求不要让现有 family 的 K 轴邻域重新主导；`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 比 `K=88` 更能回答一个新的结构问题：当前 lowrank+expert+residual 是否仍需要双 expert 才能工作。之所以值得做，是因为本轮不是把 `expert_topk` 上对单 expert 的负信号简单外推到这里，相反是利用 residual cleanup 做一次 matched-cost 复验；本地成本自检显示 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 会把总成本从 2064384 压到 1835008，约 0.49x→0.44x，信息增量明显大于继续小步压 K。主要风险是 quality 可能明显回退；若如此，也能更干净地确认当前 target 上这条 family 的低成本下限确实依赖双 expert 路由。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r152 已把 `lowrank_expert_residual` 推到 `<0.5x`：`K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 时 FVU=0.09837，当前低成本前沿最佳点已从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切换到该 family。","本地成本自检：在 r152 配方下改成 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 后，deployment_accesses=458752 不变、combined_accesses=1835008、combined_ratio≈0.44，明显左于 r152 的 2064384/0.49x，且低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是在已有有效结构上验证“单 expert + residual 是否可行”，不是把 `expert_topk` 的单 expert 负信号直接外推；它更接近当前提示要求的 matched-cost 结构性对照。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍能保持 FVU 接近或优于当前 `<0.5x` best=0.0984，则下一轮可继续只改 `K` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，把这条单 expert 路径进一步压向 0.4x 左右。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显失败，则可以更明确地记下：当前 target 上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本可用区仍依赖双 expert 路由，后续不应再在这条 family 上重复单 expert 试探。","如果该点形成新的非支配点但质量略退，则可把它作为更低成本 anchor，后续再决定是沿单 expert 分支继续压缩，还是回到新的 hetero-MoE family 做原型。"],"reference_round":152}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32234:research/history/logs/agent_round_0118.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库；在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；batch_topk、adaptive_budget_topk 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 继续明确排除。r117 已经给出负信号：在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 下，把额外预算花在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 上，只把 FVU 从 0.1464 小幅拉到 0.1440，却回到约 0.27x 成本，未形成新前沿。唯一主假设：以 r116 为 reference，只把 `K` 从 64 提到 80，在保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变时，若质量主要受限于在线查表容量而不是 routed expert 数，那么这 0.01x 左右的额外部署预算会比 r117 的 active-path 扩张更有效地回收 FVU，使该点在约 selection 0.16x + deployment 0.08x = total 0.23x 的低成本带内形成比 r116 更强、且优于“加一个 routed expert”的 matched-cost 对照。","summary":"以 r116 为 reference，保持 `shared_routed_expert_topk`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `K=80`，直接比较“加少量 lookup budget”是否比 r117 的“加 routed expert”更值得。","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"相对 r116 只改一个 env 参数 `K`，满足单变量原则。r117 已经回答了 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 这条轴的主要问题且结果偏负，因此本轮改做 deployment 轴，是合规的换轴而不是重复微调。选择 `K=80` 而不是回到更高成本点，是因为本地 cost 自检显示该点 combined_ratio 约 0.23，仍处于当前最需要补强的低成本带，同时它与 r115/r116/r117 构成很干净的 matched-cost 对照：同样是给 r116 补一点预算，本轮把预算给查表容量，不再给更多 active experts。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"80"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["实际工作区低成本 frontier 已由 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主导：r113 约 0.27x / FVU 0.1350，r115 约 0.24x / 0.1397，r116 约 0.22x / 0.1464；提示中的 `<0.5x` 摘要已明显过时。","r117 给出清晰负信号：`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3` 在 `K=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 下仅把 FVU 从 0.1464 改到 0.1440，但成本抬回约 0.27x，说明在当前 target 上继续增加 routed expert 数的边际收益很弱。","本地 cost 估算显示：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=80 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 的 selection_accesses=655360、deployment_accesses=327680、combined_accesses=983040，combined_ratio 约 0.23，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=80` 在约 0.23x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 r115，说明对当前窄 expert recipe 来说，额外预算更该给 lookup capacity 而不是更多 active routed experts；下一轮可继续在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下细化 `K=72/80/96` 的 deployment knee。","如果 `K=80` 仍只带来很小改善，则说明 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 这条 width-compression 子线已经接近质量下限，shared+routed 方向在当前 target 的低成本增益基本摸清；下一轮应换 family，而不是继续扫同一子线。","如果 `K=80` 意外接近或优于 r115，则可以判定‘窄 expert + 稍多 lookup’比‘更宽 expert + 更少 lookup’更有效；后续应优先做 matched `K`/`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 交换，而不是再碰 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3`。"],"reference_round":116}
