research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32423:research/history/round_summaries/round_0208.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r\uff1b{u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r207 \u5df2\u7ecf\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160 TRUNK_RANK=16` \u63a8\u5230 objective=0.396871\u3001cost=0.199219x\u3001exceed=0.197653\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u70b9\u4e0e incumbent r199 \u7684\u5dee\u8ddd 0.010757 \u91cc\uff0c\u7edd\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u6765\u81ea cost \u800c\u4e0d\u662f exceed\uff1b\u540c\u65f6 family \u5185\u5df2\u6709\u65c1\u8bc1 r175 vs r170 \u8868\u660e\u5728\u66f4\u9ad8 K\u3001\u66f4\u5bbd latent \u7684 recipe \u4e0a\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 16 \u538b\u5230 8 \u80fd\u4ee5\u66f4\u4f4e cost \u6362\u6765\u66f4\u4f4e objective\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u5fc5\u7136\u9020\u6210 tail error \u7206\u70b8\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r207 \u4ec5\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 16 \u538b\u5230 8\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u7528\u66f4\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 trunk \u76f4\u63a5\u62b9\u6389\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u8981\u7531 encoder cost \u5e26\u6765\u7684 objective \u7f3a\u53e3\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\uff0c`TRUNK_RANK=16 -> 8` \u4f1a\u628a combined_accesses \u4ece 835584 \u964d\u5230 778240\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u7684 actual total_cost_ratio \u4ece\u7ea6 0.199219x \u964d\u5230\u7ea6 0.185547x\uff1b\u8fd9\u610f\u5473\u7740\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u7684\u56de\u5f39\u4e0d\u8d85\u8fc7\u7ea6 0.0137\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u5c31\u4f1a\u4f18\u4e8e r207\uff0c\u800c\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u4e0d\u9ad8\u4e8e\u7ea6 0.2006\uff0c\u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u8d8a\u8fc7 incumbent r199\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32424:research/history/round_summaries/round_0208.json:36:      "\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u5df2\u901a\u8fc7\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk K=64 A=2 L=160` \u5728 `TRUNK_RANK=16` \u65f6 combined_accesses=835584\u3001actual total_cost_ratio\u22480.199219x\uff1b\u5728 `TRUNK_RANK=8` \u65f6 combined_accesses=778240\u3001actual total_cost_ratio\u22480.185547x\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32466:research/history/logs/agent_round_0149.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"revisit","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，E(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量静态 expert 子库选择 + expert 内 local top-k + 查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r148 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“expert-internal low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert、低成本 recipe 下是否能优于现有 0.20x-0.22x 低成本锚点，并形成新的结构性前沿段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该点在约 0.20x 成本下明显优于当前 0.20x-0.22x anchor，则下一轮只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K`，继续判断瓶颈在 shared basis 宽度还是 lookup 预算。","若该点仍明显劣于同成本 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 锚点，则可更明确地下调 `factorized_expert_topk` 以及相关 expert-internal low-rank 无 shared/residual 线的优先级。","若该点改善有限但比 r133 明显更好，则说明旧负信号主要受旧 recipe 影响；后续可保留该 family 作为低成本结构参考，但不应让其主导预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["r148 的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 在当前 matched recipe 下得到 FVU=0.1140，说明 trunk-free staged residual 仍未补出新的 <0.5x Pareto 段。","本地 allowlist 自检已通过：`factorized_expert_topk` 接受 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 这些当前 recipe 所需 override。","本地 smoke 已过：`factorized_expert_topk` 在 K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224 下可 instantiate 并 forward。","本地成本自检：该 recipe 下 `factorized_expert_topk` selection_ratio≈0.09、deployment_ratio≈0.11、combined_ratio≈0.20，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前 `expert_topk` 同 recipe 的约 0.23x。","旧的 r133 负信号来自不同 recipe（K=128、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320）；本轮是在当前 112/224/2-expert recipe 下做 fresh validation，不应直接把旧结果当结论。"],"reference_round":148,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r148 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。最近两轮 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 都没有形成新非支配点，继续在这些 family 上做局部旋钮微调信息增量很低；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 能在当前 matched recipe 下补一条尚未被近期复验的 expert-internal low-rank 结构证据，而且总成本仅约 0.20x，正落在当前最需要补强的低成本带。主要风险是该 family 在旧 recipe 上已有负信号，但本轮正是为了验证这些负信号是否只是旧配置下的假阴性。","summary":"建议以 r148 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.20x 低成本带的结构复验，目标不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是直接回答“expert 内 low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert recipe 下是否能形成比现有低成本锚点更有价值的新段。","touched_files":[]}
