research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32478:research/history/logs/agent_round_0149.stdout.log:691:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"revisit","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，E(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量静态 expert 子库选择 + expert 内 local top-k + 查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r148 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“expert-internal low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert、低成本 recipe 下是否能优于现有 0.20x-0.22x 低成本锚点，并形成新的结构性前沿段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该点在约 0.20x 成本下明显优于当前 0.20x-0.22x anchor，则下一轮只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K`，继续判断瓶颈在 shared basis 宽度还是 lookup 预算。","若该点仍明显劣于同成本 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 锚点，则可更明确地下调 `factorized_expert_topk` 以及相关 expert-internal low-rank 无 shared/residual 线的优先级。","若该点改善有限但比 r133 明显更好，则说明旧负信号主要受旧 recipe 影响；后续可保留该 family 作为低成本结构参考，但不应让其主导预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["r148 的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 在当前 matched recipe 下得到 FVU=0.1140，说明 trunk-free staged residual 仍未补出新的 <0.5x Pareto 段。","本地 allowlist 自检已通过：`factorized_expert_topk` 接受 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 这些当前 recipe 所需 override。","本地 smoke 已过：`factorized_expert_topk` 在 K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224 下可 instantiate 并 forward。","本地成本自检：该 recipe 下 `factorized_expert_topk` selection_ratio≈0.09、deployment_ratio≈0.11、combined_ratio≈0.20，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前 `expert_topk` 同 recipe 的约 0.23x。","旧的 r133 负信号来自不同 recipe（K=128、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320）；本轮是在当前 112/224/2-expert recipe 下做 fresh validation，不应直接把旧结果当结论。"],"reference_round":148,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r148 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。最近两轮 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 都没有形成新非支配点，继续在这些 family 上做局部旋钮微调信息增量很低；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 能在当前 matched recipe 下补一条尚未被近期复验的 expert-internal low-rank 结构证据，而且总成本仅约 0.20x，正落在当前最需要补强的低成本带。主要风险是该 family 在旧 recipe 上已有负信号，但本轮正是为了验证这些负信号是否只是旧配置下的假阴性。","summary":"建议以 r148 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.20x 低成本带的结构复验，目标不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是直接回答“expert 内 low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert recipe 下是否能形成比现有低成本锚点更有价值的新段。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32519:research/history/round_summaries/round_0200.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_expert_topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`\uff1a\u5176\u4e2d `{u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,i}}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0c\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u9700\u8ba1\u7b97\u5c11\u91cf trunk \u7cfb\u6570\u3001\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3001\u518d\u505a\u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u4e0e\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5b50\u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + \u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u6d41\u6c34\u7ebf\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002\u5f53\u524d incumbent r199 \u7684 objective=0.386114 \u7531 cost=0.19x \u4e0e exceed=0.196114 \u8fd1\u4e4e\u5bf9\u534a\u6784\u6210\uff0c\u5df2\u4e0d\u9002\u5408\u7ee7\u7eed\u53ea\u505a\u540c family \u5c0f\u63d2\u503c\uff1b\u66f4\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u662f\uff1a\u5728\u540c\u6837 small-K=`64` \u7684 very-short routed path \u4e0b\uff0c\u589e\u52a0\u4e00\u4e2a\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 low-rank trunk\uff0c\u80fd\u5426\u7528\u7ea6 +0.02x \u7684\u603b\u6210\u672c\u6362\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u591a\u7684 exceed \u964d\u5e45\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r199 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=64`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201clow-rank trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9\u66f4\u5c0f K \u4e0b\u7684 exceed_alpha_0.50 \u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e routed-only incumbent\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u5019\u9009\u7684 selection_accesses=491520\u3001deployment_accesses=409600\u3001combined_accesses=901120\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u7684 rounded total_cost_ratio=`0.21x`\uff0c\u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u5904\u4e8e `<0.25x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\uff0c\u4e5f\u8fdc\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u9884\u7b97\u3002\u5386\u53f2\u4e0a\u6700\u63a5\u8fd1\u7684\u540c family \u70b9 r187/197 \u5728\u66f4\u9ad8 `K=96`\u3001\u540c `TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001\u540c `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` \u4e0b\u5df2\u62ff\u5230 exceed\u22480.1766\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u8fd9\u8f6e\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u3001\u4e5f\u6700\u6709\u5e0c\u671b\u9a8c\u8bc1\u201c\u7528 cheap trunk \u6362 small-K exceed\u201d\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u7684 matched-objective architecture probe\u3002",
