research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32884:research/history/logs/agent_round_0145.stdout.log:892:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x) u_r 是 low-rank trunk，U={u_r} 是静态 trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“low-rank trunk 查表/加权和 + 单 expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 仍判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r143 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`、`K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试 low-rank trunk 是否已足够吃掉大部分平滑主干，使 routed 路径可以收缩到单 expert 并把 total_cost 从约 0.29x 压到约 0.24x，同时尽量保住 r143 的质量。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍明显优于当前 0.24x 左右 frontier，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，继续压缩 lowrank+expert 低成本段。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明 r143 的质量仍依赖双 expert residual capacity；后续优先保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，再考虑 `TRUNK_RANK` 的温和压缩，而不是继续削 expert 路径。","如果结果介于 r143 与当前 0.24x anchor 之间，则说明 low-rank trunk 对减少 active experts 有部分帮助但不足以完全替代双 expert；后续应更偏向带 residual 的三段式结构而不是继续把 routed path 压到极限。"],"notes_to_memory":["r143 已在约 0.29x total_cost 下形成新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` archive 点，FVU=0.1273，值得围绕它做一次非 K 轴的低成本归因。","本地 allowlist 自检通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='lowrank_expert_topk')` 接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，不会在训练前被判为 `Disallowed env override keys`。","成本自检：在 r143 配方下把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 设为 1 后，selection_accesses=376832、deployment_accesses=622592、combined_accesses=999424，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.24，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":143,"self_review":"这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r143 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。当前阶段要补的是低到中成本带的新结构性前沿，而不是继续扫 K；在 r143 已证明 `lowrank_expert_topk` 有价值后，最直接的高信息量问题就是 low-rank trunk 是否足以支撑把 routed 路径收缩到单 expert。主要风险是单 expert 会明显损失 residual 容量，导致结果回退到当前 0.24x-0.25x anchor 附近；但这正是本轮要回答的核心结构问题。","summary":"建议以 r143 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。这是一轮低成本压缩探针，直接测试 `lowrank_expert_topk` 能否把 active routed path 从双 expert 收缩到单 expert，并在约 0.24x total_cost 下维持足够接近 r143 的质量。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32885:research/history/logs/agent_round_0198.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"80"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family 保持 `expert_topk`。最终重构公式仍为 `x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`，其中 `{b_{e,i}}` 是各 expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量静态 expert 子库，再在所选子库内做 local top-k 查表与有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“子库选择 + 查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为 `直接兼容`。当前 incumbent r196 的 objective 由 cost=0.20x 与 exceed=0.1845 近乎对半构成，但最近两次更复杂结构对照并没有买到足够便宜的 exceed 改善：r197 `lowrank_expert_topk` 用 +0.03 cost 只换回 -0.0079 exceed，r191 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 也只是 +0.03 cost 换 -0.0086 exceed，说明当前前沿更像 cost 受限而不是继续加 trunk/shared 分支就会赢。相对 r196 仅把 `K` 从 96 降到 80，保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变；本地成本自检显示 deployment 访问从 393216 降到 327680，combined_accesses 从 851968 降到 786432，exact total_cost_ratio 从 0.2031 降到 0.1875。只要 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 的上升小于 0.0156，这轮 objective 就会优于 r196；这正好回答当前更关键的问题：在 active-path 已扩到 2 experts 之后，当前最佳兼容 family 是否还存在可兑现的 small-K slack。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=80` 仍能把 exceed 控在约 0.20 以内并刷新 objective，下轮继续留在 `expert_topk` 主线，只再改一个更小的 deployment 旋钮，确认 small-K knee。","如果 `K=80` 的 exceed 明显跳升、吃掉这 0.0156 的 cost 收益，则可更有把握地判定 r196 已接近该 family 的 deployment knee，后续应停止在 `expert_topk` 上线性降 K，转回新的结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["r196 当前最优点是 `expert_topk K=96 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`，objective=0.3845 由 cost 0.20x 与 exceed 0.1845 近乎对半构成，已不是纯 exceed 主导。","最近的结构扩展 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 都只拿到约 0.008 的 exceed 改善，却各自多付约 0.03 total_cost_ratio，说明在当前 0.20x-0.25x 带里，额外 trunk/shared 路径还没有证明自己值回票价。","本地成本自检：`expert_topk` 在 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 下改 `K=80` 后 selection 仍是 458752 accesses，deployment 变为 327680，combined 786432，对应 exact combined_ratio 0.1875，远低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。"],"reference_round":196,"self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r196 只改 `K`。没有新增 tunable 参数，也没有代码改动，因此不需要触碰 `sparsify/` 之外路径。之所以选 `K=80` 而不是更保守的 `88`，是因为 `88` 只省 32768 次访问，objective 增益窗口仅 0.0078，信息量偏低；而 `64` 对当前未验证的 active2 recipe 来说跨步过大。主要风险是 exceed 对 `K` 很敏感，导致 objective 反而回退；但这会直接证明当前 incumbent 已接近 small-K deployment knee。","summary":"建议以 r196 为 reference，只改 `K=80`。这不是继续围绕 FVU 做微调，而是一次针对当前 cost 略主导前沿的 deployment 压缩 probe：用最强兼容 incumbent 直接测试 active2+192 recipe 是否还能在更小 K 下保持 exceed，从而把 objective 再往下推。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:32926:research/history/logs/agent_round_0198.stdout.log:982:research/history/logs/agent_round_0191.stdout.log:3048:research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(h(x))} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(r(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff1a\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)` \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u79e9 coarse bottleneck\uff0c`{u_i}` \u662f shared/coarse \u5206\u652f\u7684\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`r(x)=x-x_coarse` \u8868\u793a\u7ecf\u7b2c\u4e00\u9636\u6bb5 shared/coarse \u91cd\u6784\u540e\u7684\u6b8b\u5dee\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f routed expert residual \u5b50\u5e93\u7684\u9759\u6001\u539f\u5b50\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u5148\u7528\u6781\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 shared low-rank/coarse \u5206\u652f\u5403\u6389\u5e73\u6ed1\u4e3b\u5e72\uff0c\u518d\u8ba9\u5c11\u91cf routed experts \u53ea\u505a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b50\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201cshared/coarse \u67e5\u8868 + routed residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u4e3a\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d frontier\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u989d\u5916\u63d0\u793a\u5df2\u628a\u95ee\u9898\u6536\u675f\u5230\u201c\u4fdd\u6301 very short active path\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u589e\u5927\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\uff0c\u5e76\u8ba9 shared/coarse branch \u8d1f\u8d23\u4e3b\u5e72\u3001routed experts \u53ea\u505a sparse residual cleanup\u201d\uff1b\u5728\u5df2\u77e5 `expert_topk` \u4e0e `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` \u90fd\u7ed9\u51fa\u65b0\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u4e0b\u4e00\u95ee\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 family \u8865 `K/LATENTS`\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7528\u4e00\u4e2a\u771f\u6b63\u6539\u53d8\u2018\u5bb9\u91cf\u4e0e\u6fc0\u6d3b\u8def\u5f84\u5173\u7cfb\u2019\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u505a matched architecture probe\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r165 \u53ea\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=108`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201ccheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup\u201d\u662f\u5426\u6bd4\u8fd1\u671f\u5931\u8d25\u7684 routed-only / fully-factorized \u65b9\u5411\u66f4\u63a5\u8fd1\u5f53\u524d low-cost anchors\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u5019\u9009\u5728\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u4e0b selection_accesses=647168\u3001deployment_accesses=442368\u3001combined_accesses=1089536\uff0c\u5bf9\u5e94 combined_ratio \u7ea6 `0.26x`\uff0c\u7565\u9ad8\u4e8e\u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u4e0a\u6cbf\u4f46\u660e\u786e\u5904\u4e8e\u5141\u8bb8\u7684 `0.25x-0.35x` \u8f85\u52a9\u5e26\u5185\uff0c\u4e5f\u663e\u8457\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
