research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34032:  "family_name": "shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34044:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，B^sh 与各 routed expert 子库 B_e 都是真正静态向量库。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection -> router 选少量 routed experts -> shared 子库 local top-k + routed 子库 local top-k -> 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表流水线，兼容性判断为直接兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是不兼容，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：当前最缺的新结构信息不是继续细扫现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是提示中明确要求的异构 MoE 新槽位“shared experts + routed experts”叠加 expert 内部 low-rank scorer。相对 r108 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到新实现的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变，直接回答“shared+routed + shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local top-k”是否能在更低 encoder 成本下保住 shared+routed 的质量优势。按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 粗估，这个结构的 selection cost 将明显低于 r108 的 full-dim shared+routed scorer，而 deployment cost 保持同量级，因此有机会把 total_cost 压到约 0.25x 左右，同时仍明显优于当前 <0.5x 区域的旧 anchor。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34045:    "summary": "已实际落盘新的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 最小原型，并完成 instantiate/forward/backward 本地 smoke。以 r108 为 matched reference，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到这个新 family，直接验证“异构 shared+routed MoE + shared low-rank basis + expert-local top-k”是否值得继续。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34048:    "family_name": "shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34050:    "self_review": "这轮不再把主要预算投入到现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的局部扫参，符合当前额外提示。代码改动限制在 `sparsify/`，没有新增 env key，也没有改执行层；新 family 复用现有 `NUM_EXPERTS / ACTIVE_EXPERTS / LATENTS_PER_EXPERT / FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 语义。为降低工程风险，我只实现最小注册链与前向/反向路径，并用 `architecture=shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk, K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 完成了本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。主要风险是该 family 虽然 scorer 更轻，但 shared low-rank basis 可能削弱 shared+routed 的表达能力；不过这正是当前最需要回答的新结构问题。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34055:        "value": "shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk"
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34063:      "本轮新增了最小可运行 family `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`：shared expert 始终激活，routed experts 由轻量 router 选择，但 shared 与 routed expert 内部都通过共享 low-rank basis `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` 做 local scoring。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0209.stdout.log:34065:      "本地 smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk', K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256)` 在 CPU 上完成 instantiate、forward、backward。",
