research/history/round_summaries/round_0223.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_J(x-trunk(x))} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c\u5373 `x_hat = trunk(x) + sparse_residual(x)`\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d `{u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_i}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`S_J(\u00b7)` \u8868\u793a\u7531 JumpReLU \u9608\u503c\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u5f97\u5230\u7684\u7a00\u758f residual \u652f\u6301\u96c6\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201clow-rank trunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + JumpReLU residual \u9009\u62e9 + residual \u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u662f\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar222 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5bf9 plain `lowrank_residual` \u7ed9\u51fa\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u5e76\u6ca1\u6709\u56de\u7b54 residual \u4e3b\u7ebf\u5931\u8d25\u5230\u5e95\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a trunk+residual \u5206\u89e3\u672c\u8eab\u4e0d\u6210\u7acb\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u666e\u901a top-k residual \u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u65b9\u5f0f\u8fc7\u4e8e\u7c97\u7cd9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4ee5\u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u53ea\u6539 residual \u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\uff0c\u4e0d\u6539\u6210\u672c\u91cf\u7ea7\uff0cJumpReLU \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u964d\u4f4e exceed\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1081344\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=1327104\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.31640625\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.15234375\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d anchor\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.0391312575`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4f9d\u7136\u6781\u5176\u6fc0\u8fdb\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u672c\u8f6e\u4e0d\u662f\u73b0\u5b9e\u7684\u593a\u51a0\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u7ed3\u6784\u88c1\u51b3\uff1a\u5982\u679c JumpReLU \u5728\u4e0e `lowrank_residual` \u76f8\u540c\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u4ecd\u4e0d\u80fd\u628a exceed \u663e\u8457\u62c9\u4f4e\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 residual-support-formation \u8fd9\u6761\u5206\u652f\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u4e00\u5e76\u964d\u7ea7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}。其中 shared 子库 B^sh 与 routed expert 子库 {B_e} 都是静态向量库，在线侧只做轻量 router 选择少量 routed experts，然后执行 shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍明确不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。当前 `<0.25x` 主战场里，r115→r116 已证明 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 在保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的前提下沿 width 轴左移仍有结构信号，而 r114 又给出清晰负信号：把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 压到 1 虽能到约 0.20x，但 FVU 会退化到 0.2038。唯一主假设是：相对 r116 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 192 再压到 160，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_expert_topk`、`K=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，可以把 total_cost 从约 0.22x 再左移到约 0.20x，而避免重蹈 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的质量崩塌；若 FVU 仍明显优于 r114 并尽量接近 r116，则说明在当前 target 上，进一步压每-expert 宽度比压 active experts 更值得作为 `<0.25x` 主线继续推进。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:20:    "summary": "以 r116 为 reference，保持当前最强 low-cost baseline `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 `K=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`。这是一轮严格落在 `<0.25x` 主战场的 matched-cost 轻量化 probe，直接回答在约 0.20x total_cost 下，shared+routed 结构是否能通过更窄 expert 子库打败现有同成本 anchors，而不必退回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:25:    "self_review": "相对 r116 只改一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，满足单变量原则。当前策略已经明确把主战场收缩到 `<0.25x`，因此不应再让 0.5x 左右结构主导预算；沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 这条现有最强 low-cost baseline 做 matched light variant，比再开一个天然落到中成本区的新 family 更符合本轮目标。之所以选 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 而不是继续降 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或直接降 `K`，是因为 r114 已证明 active-path 再压会明显伤害质量，而，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:35:      "r114 已给出负锚点：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256` 在约 0.20x total_cost 下退化到 FVU 0.2038，说明当前 low-cost 质量不适合继续压 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:36:      "r116 已给出当前最直接的宽度锚点：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 在约 0.22x total_cost 下达到 FVU 0.1464，因此相对它继续把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 压到 160 是当前 `<0.25x` 带内最干净的单变量后续问题。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0159.json:38:      "本轮不需要代码修改；`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 与 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 wiring 已在历史轮次中稳定生效。"
