research/history/round_summaries/round_0190.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r187 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。选择这条轴而不是继续改 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，是因为当前策略明确要求避免在同一 family 上继续做线性插值点，而 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 直接改变 active path 长度，属于更高信息量的结构性压缩。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk` 而不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线，是因为后者已被明确降为 cost anchor；选择它而不是再开一个新的 factorized/shared-lowrank architecture family，是因为 r186-r189 已连续给出这些方向的 fresh 负信号。主要风险是同 target 的旧 recipe 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的单 expert 版本已经出现过明显负信号；但那条证据对应的是更重的 `K=112, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, TRUNK_RANK=40` 配方。当前这一轮要回答的是更轻 `K=96, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192, TRUNK_RANK=16` recipe 下，trunk 是否已经足以支撑更短 active path，而这在当前成本带上仍未被直接验证。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0190.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r187 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。选择这条轴而不是继续改 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，是因为当前策略明确要求避免在同一 family 上继续做线性插值点，而 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 直接改变 active path 长度，属于更高信息量的结构性压缩。选择 `lowrank_expert_topk` 而不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线，是因为后者已被明确降为 cost anchor；选择它而不是再开一个新的 factorized/shared-lowrank architecture family，是因为 r186-r189 已连续给出这些方向的 fresh 负信号。主要风险是同 target 的旧 recipe 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的单 expert 版本已经出现过明显负信号；但那条证据对应的是更重的 `K=112, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, TRUNK_RANK=40` 配方。当前这一轮要回答的是更轻 `K=96, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192, TRUNK_RANK=16` recipe 下，trunk 是否已经足以支撑更短 active path，而这在当前成本带上仍未被直接验证。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0177.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r176 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。选择 r176 而不是 r165，是为了把比较聚焦在刚得到的新负信号上，直接回答“routed-only 失败后，加回一个 shared branch 是否能在不抬高成本带的前提下恢复质量”。这比回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线继续做局部 `K/LATENTS` 插值更符合当前策略，也比再试一次已经连续偏弱的 `factorized_expert_topk` 更有解释力。主要风险是该 family 在历史上已有低成本负信号；但若不做这一步，就无法干净区分当前失败究竟来自缺 shared branch，还是来自 factorized hetero-MoE 结构本身。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0177.json:41:      "如果 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下明显优于 r176 的 `expert_topk`，但仍落后于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors，则说明 shared branch 确有价值，但 routed/full-head 被一并 factorize 后损失过大；后续应继续下调 fully factorized hetero-MoE 方向优先级。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0177.json:64:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r176 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。选择 r176 而不是 r165，是为了把比较聚焦在刚得到的新负信号上，直接回答“routed-only 失败后，加回一个 shared branch 是否能在不抬高成本带的前提下恢复质量”。这比回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线继续做局部 `K/LATENTS` 插值更符合当前策略，也比再试一次已经连续偏弱的 `factorized_expert_topk` 更有解释力。主要风险是该 family 在历史上已有低成本负信号；但若不做这一步，就无法干净区分当前失败究竟来自缺 shared branch，还是来自 factorized hetero-MoE 结构本身。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0219.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0219.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_shared(h(x))} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)` \u662f shared low-rank bottleneck\uff0c`{u_i}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 shared/coarse \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_{e,j}}` \u662f routed expert \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201cshared low-rank \u4e3b\u5e72\u67e5\u8868 + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + routed \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u662f\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar217 \u5df2\u5f3a\u70c8\u5426\u5b9a\u201cfactorized shared+routed scorer\u201d\uff0cr218 \u53c8\u5426\u5b9a\u4e86\u201cshared low-rank coarse + two-stage residual cleanup\u201d\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5f53\u524d remaining matched probe \u91cc\u552f\u4e00\u4ecd\u843d\u5728 `0.18x~0.22x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u3001\u4e14\u8fd8\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u672a\u51b3\u95ee\u9898\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u662f\u66f4\u7b80\u5355\u7684 `shared low-rank trunk + routed experts`\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4ee5\u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cshared low-rank trunk \u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u4fdd\u7559\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u4e00\u65e6\u53bb\u6389 explicit residual cleanup \u5c31\u4f1a\u518d\u6b21\u8ba9 exceed \u5931\u63a7\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=737280\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=901120\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.21484375\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.05078125\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d anchor\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.1406937575`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4f9d\u7136\u5f88\u9ad8\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u81f3\u5c11\u7528\u4e00\u4e2a\u4ecd\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\u7684 probe\uff0c\u5e72\u51c0\u88c1\u51b3 `shared low-rank trunk + routed experts` \u8fd9\u6761\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u4ef7\u503c\u3002",
