research/history/round_summaries/round_0226.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `jumprelu`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `S_\u03c4(x)` \u7531 JumpReLU \u9608\u503c\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u7ed9\u51fa\uff0c`{b_i}` \u662f\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e2d\u7684\u539f\u5b50\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201c\u9608\u503c\u5316\u9009\u62e9 + \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u5c5e\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1aRound 220 \u7684 `factorized_topk` \u4e0e Round 225 \u7684 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5df2\u7ecf\u628a\u201c\u66f4\u8f7b scorer/router\u201d\u65b9\u5411\u88c1\u6210\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u800c `0.21x` \u4e00\u5e26\u7684 shared/coarse/lowrank \u67b6\u6784\u4e5f\u672a\u80fd\u6362\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u4f4e\u7684 exceed\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `jumprelu`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4ee5\u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u5728\u4e0d\u5f15\u5165\u66f4\u957f active path\u3001\u4e5f\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0 deployment \u590d\u6742\u5ea6\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u7eaf\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u53d8\u5316\u80fd\u5426\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584 `exceed_alpha_0.50`\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1048576\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=1212416\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.2890625\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 r212 \u7684 objective=0.35553750753402713\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed_alpha_0.50 \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.06647500753402712`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u5f88\u6fc0\u8fdb\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u4ecd\u7136\u6bd4\u5f53\u524d\u5269\u4f59\u90a3\u4e9b `0.38x+`\u3001\u5728 objective \u4e0a\u5df2\u5148\u9a8c\u4e0d\u53ef\u80fd\u7ffb\u76d8\u7684\u672a\u6d4b family \u66f4\u6709\u73b0\u5b9e\u610f\u4e49\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5b83\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u5269\u4f59\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u91cc\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u4e2a\u4ecd\u5177\u975e\u96f6 objective \u8d62\u9762\u3001\u4e14\u80fd\u5e72\u51c0\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u95ee\u9898\u5230\u5e95\u5728\u8def\u7531/\u5b50\u5e93\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5728\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u201d \u7684 matched architecture probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0226.json:36:      "\u5f53\u524d `0.19x~0.21x` matched architecture probes \u4e5f\u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u90fd\u6ca1\u628a objective \u62c9\u56de r212 \u9644\u8fd1\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(h(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态向量库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared+routed 异构 MoE 中把 expert 内部 scorer 也做低秩化”是否能在约 0.22x total_cost 下形成新的低成本结构段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:35:      "r141 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 在约 0.30x total_cost 下仍被当前 low-cost frontier 压制，因此“shared low-rank basis + full expert head”这条无 residual 线可暂时降级。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:42:      "如果结果只小幅优于 `expert_topk` 但仍被 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 支配，则说明 shared branch 有价值，但 routed experts 过度低秩化会伤害质量；后续应优先保留 expert-specific full heads 或切向别的 staged/residual 结构。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:87:    "ARCHITECTURE": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:35:      "r155 已落盘：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 实际 FVU=0.14630839228630066，显著落后当前 0.28x-0.30x 低成本 frontier，因此不应继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:39:      "这轮是对另一条高优先级结构槽位 `two-stage residual expert` 的 matched-cost 重验，不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或已失败的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。"
